<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 20:07:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“我发现自己感到非常害怕”：随着加沙战争后反犹太主义的蔓延，美国的犹太人保持低调</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-in-america-lie-low-as-antisemitism-spirals-in-wake-of-gaza-war/0000018b-b404-d3c1-a39b-bee5c5550000</link><description>犹太裔美国人有生以来第一次感到有必要隐藏自己的宗教和种族身份。一些人解释了原因，而另一些人则透露了为什么尽管一些城市普遍存在反以色列情绪，但他们拒绝掩饰自己的犹太身份</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:53:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/jews-in-america-lie-low-as-antisemitism-spirals-in-wake-of-gaza-war/0000018b-b404-d3c1-a39b-bee5c5550000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯兰圣战组织发布了以色列男孩和老年妇女被绑架到加沙的视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/islamic-jihad-releases-video-of-israeli-boy-and-elderly-woman-kidnapped-into-gaza/0000018b-b57f-dedf-adab-f57f55630000</link><description>视频中的主角是 13 岁的亚吉尔·雅科夫 (Yagil Yaakov) 和 77 岁的汉娜·卡齐尔 (Hanna Katzir)，两人都来自尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz)。该恐怖组织表示，出于人道主义原因，他们准备释放人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:43:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/islamic-jihad-releases-video-of-israeli-boy-and-elderly-woman-kidnapped-into-gaza/0000018b-b57f-dedf-adab-f57f55630000</guid></item><item><title>加沙一名士兵的感想：我们还会在这里看到多少次日出？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-soldiers-thoughts-in-gaza-how-many-more-sunrises-will-we-see-here/0000018b-b3ef-dedf-adab-f7ff52b50000</link><description>经过一个月的预备役服役后，这里没有英雄主义的故事，几乎没有阵雨，但有很多问题。我第一次回家几个小时，一切都感觉不一样了。甚至我的孩子们。也许我也是</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 19:09:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-soldiers-thoughts-in-gaza-how-many-more-sunrises-will-we-see-here/0000018b-b3ef-dedf-adab-f7ff52b50000</guid></item><item><title>整个以色列家庭被哈马斯关押：“三代人坐在地下”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/entire-israeli-families-held-by-hamas-three-generations-sitting-underground/0000018b-b3d3-dea2-a9bf-f3df988c0000</link><description>被关押在加沙的五个家庭的亲属向《国土报》讲述了他们生命中最糟糕的四个星期</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 18:17:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/entire-israeli-families-held-by-hamas-three-generations-sitting-underground/0000018b-b3d3-dea2-a9bf-f3df988c0000</guid></item><item><title>在战争中，以色列左派发现自己真正孤独</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-09/ty-article/.highlight/in-war-israeli-leftists-find-themselves-truly-alone/0000018b-b52b-d3c1-a39b-bfeb9d690000</link><description>打击对阿拉伯人、巴勒斯坦人和其他少数民族的迫害是一场艰苦的战斗。当我们同时必须提醒我们所谓的盟友我们也被允许存在时，这就变得更加困难</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 18:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-11-09/ty-article/.highlight/in-war-israeli-leftists-find-themselves-truly-alone/0000018b-b52b-d3c1-a39b-bfeb9d690000</guid></item><item><title>你会吃一块含有假脂肪的饼干来拯救地球吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-09/ty-article/would-you-eat-a-cookie-with-fake-fat-to-save-the-planet/0000018b-b4a0-dedf-adab-f5b0fc850000</link><description>您很可能不知道馅饼皮从哪里来并且不在乎，那么您会改用人造油来拯救地球吗？</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 17:12:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2023-11-09/ty-article/would-you-eat-a-cookie-with-fake-fat-to-save-the-planet/0000018b-b4a0-dedf-adab-f5b0fc850000</guid></item><item><title>非法接管 30 年后，高等法院命令定居者离开巴勒斯坦土地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/30-years-after-illegal-takeover-high-court-orders-settlers-out-of-palestinian-land/0000018b-b4db-dea2-a9bf-f4dfdc120000</link><description>以色列定居者一直在这片土地上种植椰枣，法院裁定这片土地是非法移交给他们的。法院表示，这种种植行为“不仅违反了国际法和政府宣布的政策，甚至违反了哈拉克法”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:40:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/30-years-after-illegal-takeover-high-court-orders-settlers-out-of-palestinian-land/0000018b-b4db-dea2-a9bf-f4dfdc120000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德和中央情报局局长会见卡塔尔总理讨论人质交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-cia-chiefs-meet-with-qatari-pm-to-discuss-hostage-deal/0000018b-b4af-dea2-a9bf-f4bf183a0000</link><description>据报道，会谈包括关于暂停加沙战斗和允许向飞地进口人道主义燃料的讨论，以换取释放 10 至 15 名以色列人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:38:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/mossad-cia-chiefs-meet-with-qatari-pm-to-discuss-hostage-deal/0000018b-b4af-dea2-a9bf-f4bf183a0000</guid></item><item><title>民意调查显示，四分之三的美国犹太人因以色列与哈马斯的战争而担心自己的安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-u-s-jews-fear-for-their-safety-because-of-israel-hamas-war-poll-shows/0000018b-b4e1-df42-a78f-bde312120000</link><description>在为北美犹太联合会进行的一项民意调查中，三分之二的犹太裔美国人将他们社区的气氛描述为紧张、不舒服或可怕</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:31:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/three-quarters-of-u-s-jews-fear-for-their-safety-because-of-israel-hamas-war-poll-shows/0000018b-b4e1-df42-a78f-bde312120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军主席：巴勒斯坦权力机构每天都在努力阻止支持哈马斯的示威活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-palestinian-authority-works-daily-to-prevent-demonstrations-in-support-of-hamas/0000018b-b496-dea2-a9bf-f49e87590000</link><description>以色列国防军参谋长赫茨尔·哈勒维回应了一名极右翼议员，后者在没有证据的情况下声称巴勒斯坦权力机构可能会加入战斗，以此作为与哈马斯团结的标志</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 16:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/idf-chief-palestinian-authority-works-daily-to-prevent-demonstrations-in-support-of-hamas/0000018b-b496-dea2-a9bf-f49e87590000</guid></item><item><title>艾米·舒默因在加沙战争中为以色列而战而受到批评</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amy-schumer-draws-fire-for-coming-out-fighting-for-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018b-b43f-df42-a78f-bd7f0b260000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，这位犹太喜剧演员一直是以色列在好莱坞最强有力的倡导者。然而，她的社交媒体帖子让她被指控“仇恨巴勒斯坦人和穆斯林”以及“盗用”马丁·路德·金。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 15:49:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/amy-schumer-draws-fire-for-coming-out-fighting-for-israel-in-gaza-war/0000018b-b43f-df42-a78f-bd7f0b260000</guid></item><item><title>越来越多的以色列士兵正在记录并公布他们自己对巴勒斯坦人的虐待行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/growing-number-of-idf-soldiers-are-documenting-and-posting-their-own-abuse-of-palestinians/0000018b-ae60-dea2-a9bf-fefe96070000</link><description>在社交媒体视频中，以色列士兵殴打和羞辱巴勒斯坦被拘留者，其中一些人在受到虐待后不久就被释放。以色列国防军则对部分案件的肇事者进行了惩罚，称这种行为违反了军队价值观</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 15:21:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/growing-number-of-idf-soldiers-are-documenting-and-posting-their-own-abuse-of-palestinians/0000018b-ae60-dea2-a9bf-fefe96070000</guid></item><item><title>以色列女子涉嫌在MK家附近喷漆“1,400”，警方询问她投票给谁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-spraying-1-400-near-home-of-mk-asked-by-police-who-she-voted-for/0000018b-b40c-d3c1-a39b-beed5ffa0000</link><description>在审讯中，以色列警方询问嫌疑人耶尔·阿巴迪·赖斯 (Yael Abadi Reiss)，她在 10 月 7 日做了什么，以及她是否投票给以色列现任政府。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:47:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-spraying-1-400-near-home-of-mk-asked-by-police-who-she-voted-for/0000018b-b40c-d3c1-a39b-beed5ffa0000</guid></item><item><title>“使用武力永远不会有助于和平”：亚美尼亚总统会谈纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫、伊朗和以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-force-will-never-contribute-to-peace-an-interview-with-armenias-president/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff0a310000</link><description>亚美尼亚总统瓦哈格恩·哈恰图良（Vahagn Khachaturyan）的同胞因阿塞拜疆的闪电袭击而逃离纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫，几周后他希望两国之间实现持久和平。他还渴望与以色列建立更好的关系：“我们作为国家非常相似。我们俩都在种族灭绝中幸存下来。我们知道这意味着什么&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:38:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/using-force-will-never-contribute-to-peace-an-interview-with-armenias-president/0000018b-b3bd-df42-a78f-bfff0a310000</guid></item><item><title>据报道以色列袭击后大马士革国际机场关闭一个月</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/damascus-intl-airport-shut-for-a-month-following-reported-israeli-strikes/0000018b-b3e9-df42-a78f-bfebf9590000</link><description>这是自罢工开始以来该设施停运时间最长的一次。叙利亚和伊朗航空公司现在飞往俄罗斯空军部署地拉塔基亚</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 14:09:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/damascus-intl-airport-shut-for-a-month-following-reported-israeli-strikes/0000018b-b3e9-df42-a78f-bfebf9590000</guid></item><item><title>支持和反以色列的示威者在洛杉矶放映哈马斯暴行镜头外发生冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/pro-anti-israel-demonstrators-clash-outside-l-a-screening-of-hamas-atrocity-footage/0000018b-b412-dea2-a9bf-f49e78140000</link><description>在宽容博物馆举行的放映是众多私人放映之一，旨在让舆论制造者了解哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击以色列边境社区的残酷程度</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:54:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/pro-anti-israel-demonstrators-clash-outside-l-a-screening-of-hamas-atrocity-footage/0000018b-b412-dea2-a9bf-f49e78140000</guid></item><item><title>一个更加军事化的以色列将是一个不那么繁荣的国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/a-more-militarized-israel-will-be-a-less-prosperous-one/0000018b-b449-dea2-a9bf-f4df86f50000</link><description>加沙战争大规模调动储备金对经济产生了深远影响。战后以色列将需要他们继续服役</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:49:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/a-more-militarized-israel-will-be-a-less-prosperous-one/0000018b-b449-dea2-a9bf-f4df86f50000</guid></item><item><title>新闻机构对以色列关于哈马斯大屠杀共谋的指控提出异议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/news-agencies-dispute-israeli-allegations-of-complicity-in-hamas-massacre/0000018b-b406-dea2-a9bf-f49e606b0000</link><description>亲以色列媒体监管机构的报告很快被以色列外交部采纳，声称这些新闻媒体“在 10 月 7 日的大屠杀期间让记者与哈马斯恐怖分子混在一起”。 《纽约时报》认为这些指控“鲁莽、不真实且令人愤慨”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 13:48:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/news-agencies-dispute-israeli-allegations-of-complicity-in-hamas-massacre/0000018b-b406-dea2-a9bf-f49e606b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人厌恶内塔尼亚胡。但对与巴勒斯坦人实现和平的绝望感更深</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israelis-loathe-netanyahu-but-despair-over-peace-with-palestinians-runs-even-deeper/0000018b-b3d1-d3c1-a39b-bff181c30000</link><description>随着内塔尼亚胡的支持率跌至历史低点，10月7日哈马斯袭击后的以色列民意调查显示，战后结束血腥的巴以冲突的希望更加黯淡</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:44:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israelis-loathe-netanyahu-but-despair-over-peace-with-palestinians-runs-even-deeper/0000018b-b3d1-d3c1-a39b-bff181c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方解雇了拒绝与本·格维尔一起参加活动的安全志愿者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-remove-security-volunteer-for-refusing-to-attend-event-with-ben-gvir/0000018b-b3c8-dea2-a9bf-f3ded5cb0000</link><description>这位志愿者向《国土报》解释说：“我不会在拍完照片后就看到自己出现在本-格维尔的竞选活动中。”据他透露，警方一开始声称只有在与部长一起的仪式上才能向他发放枪支</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 Nov 2023 12:37:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-09/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-remove-security-volunteer-for-refusing-to-attend-event-with-ben-gvir/0000018b-b3c8-dea2-a9bf-f3ded5cb0000</guid></item></channel></rss>